## 🏗️ CI/CD Flow Diagram

```
Developer pushes code
        |
    GitHub Repo
        |
   GitHub Webhook
        |
   Jenkins triggered
        |
  ┌─────────────────────────────┐
  |      Jenkins Pipeline       |
  |  Stage 1: Clone from GitHub |
  |  Stage 2: Build Docker Image|
  |  Stage 3: Run Container     |
  └─────────────────────────────┘
        |
  Application Running in Docker Container
```

